headline: KeyBank Appoints Robert Weiss to Lead Family Wealth Business
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) announced that Robert Weiss has joined the company as Head of Key Family Wealth where he will collaborate across the enterprise to grow the ultra-high net worth client segment. He is based in New York City and reports to Key Wealth President Joe Skarda.
